	<h1>A Public Health Perspective on Sea-Level Rise: Starting Points for Climate Change Adaptation</h1>

	<div class="reference-info">
		
        
<p><a href="##" onClick='window.open ("http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/PIP_Journal.cfm?pip_jrnl=233596","PIP","toolbar=yes,menubar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,width=500,height=350");' class='btn-link'> Widener Law Review, Vol. 15, No. 2, pp. 521-540, 2010</a></p> <p><a href="##" onClick='window.open ("http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/PIP_Journal.cfm?pip_jrnl=219958","PIP","toolbar=yes,menubar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,width=500,height=350");' class='btn-link'> FSU College of Law, Public Law Research Paper No. 307</a></p> 

