	<h2><A HREF=https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/cf_dev/AbsByAuth.cfm?per_id=223637 target='_blank' title='View other papers by this author'>Robin Kundis Craig </a></h2><p>University of Utah S.J. Quinney College of Law</p>

